呢本書，但出文唔使太耐"},{"pid":"b236827707e954998362c40bb27e2e7e5b52461a","tid":2015233,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964823ab1f836d1d6bc5b84cc3b71ae09bd8fde7","tid":2015233,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c712167d598ec7025a55afcecddec357e55ed4d9","tid":2015233,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6799ca664b1803b6e238b4344295ed77317ebd6e","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"61c29dff85455b79b6e1d8810bfeba87a108cef6","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9eac13803b46d17032123fec22ab4c42aaee53","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"這是我最後想對連登巴絲打的話：<br />\n<br />\n沒錯，黑暗和罪惡都是由內到外鐵一般的事實（我無法想像我筆下的小說情節竟然逐漸成為事實），但是主耶穌的死和復活，以及升天都是！<br />\n<br />\n我不知道我有沒有可能活到香港光復的一天，但是有一件事比香港光復更美；就是主耶穌回來光復這個世界，我希望你到時也在那裡。"},{"pid":"3248b7382ff900adfe58695fa171ecda70a78ab7","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f664d573a1ee9cc02d1cace32ef2af2bbd23308","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a9eac13803b46d17032123fec22ab4c42aaee53","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"這是我最後想對連登巴絲打的話：<br />\n<br />\n沒錯，黑暗和罪惡都是由內到外鐵一般的事實（我無法想像我筆下的小說情節竟然逐漸成為事實），但是主耶穌的死和復活，以及升天都是！<br />\n<br />\n我不知道我有沒有可能活到香港光復的一天，但是有一件事比香港光復更美；就是主耶穌回來光復這個世界，我希望你到時也在那裡。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"我承認我因為今日的苦難看不清將來，但那是真的"},{"pid":"85bbcbb36b38143390fb4e7b0c4bb5e592c30b3a","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"1a9eac13803b46d17032123fec22ab4c42aaee53","tid":2015233,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:41:14.000Z","msg":"這是我最後想對連登巴絲打的話：<br />\n<br />\n沒錯，黑暗和罪惡都是由內到外鐵一般的事實（我無法想像我筆下的小說情節竟然逐漸成為事實），但是主耶穌的死和復活，以及升天都是！<br />\n<br />\n我不知道我有沒有可能活到香港光復的一天，但是有一件事比香港光復更美；就是主耶穌回來光復這個世界，我希望你到時也在那裡。"}}